quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  7,73,"Samuudfoͻ no nso (Yε’somaa) wͻn nua Soalih maa no kͻͻ wͻn hͻ. Ɔkaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, monsom Nyankopͻn, na monni awurade foforͻ biara wͻ N’akyi. Ampa sε (Nokorε) pefee fri mo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ aba mo hͻ; woi yε Nyankopͻn yoma bedeε a ͻyε nsεnkyerεnee ma mo; enti monyae no ma no nidi wͻ Nyankopͻn asaase no so, na monhwε na moanyε no bͻne, anyε saa a asotwee a εyε ya paa bεsͻ mo mu"
  7,74,"Monkae εberε a Ɔyεε mo ananmusifoͻ wͻ Aadfoͻ no akyi, de mo tenaa asaase no soͻ, na mosisii mo abansoroͻ wͻ ne petee no mu, san bͻne mmepͻ mu yεε no adan. Enti monkae Nyankopͻn adom, na monhwε yie na moanni nsεmͻnee wͻ asaase no so"
  7,75,"Nhemfo (anaa mpanimfoͻ) a wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ wͻ ne nkorͻfoͻ no mu no ka kyerεε wͻn a wͻ’yε mmrε na wͻ’agye adi wͻ wͻn mu no sε: “Monim sε Soalh yε obia ne Wura Nyankopͻn na asoma no? “Wͻ’kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yε’gye deε yεde asoma no no di”"
  7,76,"Wͻn a wͻ’yε ahomasoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yε’deε, yεnnye deε mogye die no nni “"
  7,77,"Enti wͻ’kum yoma bedeε no, na wͻ’tee wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn ahyεdeε no so atua, kaa sε: “Soalh, fa deε w’ahyε yεn ho bͻ no bra, sε woka (Nyame) asomafoͻ no ho ampa a”"
  7,78,"Enti asaase wosoͻ sͻͻ wͻn mu, na wͻ’yεε dinn wͻ wͻn afie mu"
  7,79,"Enti (Soalh) danee ne ho fri wͻn ho kaa sε: “Menkorͻfoͻ, mebͻͻ mo me Wura Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho dawuro kyerεε mo, na metuu mo fo, nanso moampε afotuo no”"
  7,80,"Ɛna Lut nso, εberε a ͻka kyerεε ne nkorͻfoͻ no sε: “Mobͻ ahohwi bra a amansan no mu biara nnii moanim kan nyεε bi da?”"
  7,81,"“Nokorε sε, mofri mmaa akyi de akͻnnͻ kͻ mmarima ho. Daabi, moyε nnipa a modi nsεmᴐne.”"
  7,82,"Ne nkorͻfoͻ no mmuaeε a wͻ’de maeε ara nesε: “Montu wͻn mfri mo kuro no mu; efrisε, wͻ’yε nipa a wͻ’pε ahoteε“"
  7,83,"Enti Yε’gyee ͻne n’abusuafoͻ nkwa, gyesε neyere, na ͻka wͻn a wͻ’kaa akyire no ho"
  7,84,Na Yε’tͻͻ nsuo paa gu wͻn so. Enti hwε sεdeε abͻneεfoͻ no awieε si wieε